data.description: Home Sweet Home!  Charming 3 bedroom, 2 bath home built in 2020.  The house displays modern color schemes throughout, it shows like a model home.  The Kitchen is nicely upgraded with Stainless Steel appliances, Granite countertops, an ample Island, a decorative tile backsplash and recessed lighting.  The Master Bathroom and 2nd bath are also nicely upgraded with granite countertops.  Other upgrades include: Ceramic Tiles throughout the living areas, a Water Softener and a Reverse Osmosis Water Purification System.  The Solar Panels make this home energy efficient providing great savings.  The screened-in Lanai is perfect to enjoy the outdoors anytime of the day.  Close proximity to many Shopping Centers, Restaurants and Disney Theme Parks.  SELLER WILL CONTRIBUTE $10,000 TOWARDS BUYER'S CLOSING COST OR A RATE BUYDOWN.
